name: UDEPRECATED_RigVMArrayNode
doc:
The Array Node represents one of a series available
array operations such as SetNum, GetAtIndex etc.

methods.name: GetCPPType
methods.doc: Returns the C++ data type of the element

methods.name: GetCPPTypeObject
methods.doc: Returns the C++ data type struct of the array (or nullptr)

methods.name: GetOpCode
methods.doc: Returns the op code of this node
